PubChem,provides,information,on,the,biological,activities,of,small,molecules,and,stores,them,across,three,databases,PubChem,also,provides,a,fast,chemical,structure,similarity,search,tool,The,PubChem,Power,User,Gateway,PUG,provides,access,to,PubChem,services,via,a,programmatic,interface,The,API,uses,HTTP,post,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML